  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will investigate whether probiotics given just before and shortly after major
      abdominal operation improve outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Perioperative probiotic intervention is associated with approximately 30% reduction of
      primary outcome measure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
